title: Ep49: Monogamish Gays feat a Male Gay Couple
itunes:title: Ep49: Monogamish Gays feat a Male Gay Couple
description:
While Mandii is away enjoying the NBA All Star festivities in LA, Weezy holds it down in the studio and is joined by a gay male couple who has been together for 3 years. This episode is "gay af"! Literally...that's the Whoreible Decision. Find out what it's like to be a gay couple, having sex, and wtf being monogomish means. If you're looking for another podcast and interested in traveling on a budget, subscribe to Travel GUYdes, a podcast that shares the ins and outs of traveling on a dime.
